§ 9. capitolinam arcem] This seems to he a general expression for the whole Mons Capitolinus. The two summm, Capitolium (S.W.) and Arx (N.E.), are distinguished below; between these two summits was the depression known as inter duos lucos. See rnap.

§ 10. in campo Martio] The regular place of meeting for the Comitia Centuriam, which, as a military assembly, had to be convened outside the pomerium.
